formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
This is a government project the books of accounts are maintained on cash basis hence whatever expenses are claimed as incurred and paid is either claimed basis the earlier certificate or the debit transactions in the bank statement made available to us and to ascertain the cost management representation is relied upon. 
Previous consultant had taken registration of the project and submitted CA Certificate in offline mode hence the details of the registration was not made available to us by the management . We have taken construction cost as per form 2 and other estimation as per the management. This project being govt project land is provided by the government and hence there is no land cost available in the project cost.  Promoter is maintaining a single RERA Account and hence all the amounts of booking are deposited in the same account. Booking Details KYC ID Mobile number of the allottee etc is taken as provided by the management . Details pertaining to the carpet area/ balcony area etc is taken as provided by the management. We do not take the responsibility of the KYC Id of the allottees in the absence of the sufficient documents. RERA Bank details are taken as provided by the management.The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation. As informed to us by the management there is no loan or encumbrance either on the project or on the units offered to sale. In absence of the details we have taken the booking amount received as withdrawl amount.Amount incurred and paid for expenses is taken as per the payments made in bank statement. Promoter follows the cash basis of accounting and we have relied upon the bank statement for all the financial data. bANK Balance was incorrectly entered in the last quarter which has been corrected now. booking details and received amount is taken as provided by the management. same is the case with the expenditure incurred the total debit side of bank account accumulates up to 50 cr which is in excess of estimation
